Description: Proof-of-work blockchain implementation
 XAI is a Python-based proof-of-work blockchain implementation with a UTXO
 transaction model, REST API, and wallet CLI.
  * Prometheus metrics and monitoring
 .
 This package includes the node daemon, wallet CLI, and all necessary tools
 to run a full XAI blockchain node.

