Description: Development tools for XAI Blockchain
 This package contains development tools and dependencies for building
 and testing XAI blockchain applications.
 .
 Includes:
  * Testing frameworks (pytest, pytest-cov, pytest-mock)
  * Code quality tools (black, pylint, mypy, isort)
  * Security analysis tools (bandit)
  * Property-based testing (hypothesis)

